ion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00000=
0; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Here is a tweet</a>=
 from law professor Aaron Wright that summarizes the effect[3]:</p><!--[if =
mso]>
