 style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Tokens translate social capital into economic ca=
pital. This financialization of everything has its downsides (there should =
be protections when investing in a person's token) but tokens can also boot=
strap liquidity for a creator &amp; deliver that creator's community econom=
ic upside.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And here is an <a h=
ref=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26123257.256657/aHR0cH=
