xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">like Step=
hen Diehl</a> =E2=80=94=C2=A0that =E2=80=9Cif there is any innovation in cr=
ypto assets it=E2=80=99s not in software engineering, but in financial engi=
neering,=E2=80=9D that Web3 is not about building good products in a good w=
ay but about the promise of riches.=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/26123257.256657/aHR0cHM6Ly93b2xmLmNtLmJsb29tYmVyZy5j=
