/a>, but the reverse is also true: Each cohort gets rich because a new coho=
rt gets involved.=C2=A0If the product itself is good and enjoyable to use t=
hat is probably a plus, but I am not sure it=E2=80=99s essential.</p><p sty=
le=3D"margin: 16px 0;">What sort of incentives does this create to spend yo=
ur time making=C2=A0good products?[4] Not none! But =E2=80=A6=C2=A0attenuat=
